00:21:09.664 --> 00:21:10.791
Namanya Kim Jeong-gwon.

00:21:12.042 --> 00:21:13.710
Kim Jeong-gwon?

00:21:13.794 --> 00:21:14.836
Ngomong-ngomong,

00:21:16.463 --> 00:21:17.422
siapakah awak?

